{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.1","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:1","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.011.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Guerriers qui s\u2019attach\u00e8rent \u00e0 David pendant la vie de Sa\u00fcl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-22: cf. (1 S 27; 29; 30.) 1 Th 1:7. Ps 18:47, 48.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Voici ceux qui se rendirent aupr\u00e8s de David \u00e0 Tsiklag, lorsqu\u2019il \u00e9tait encore \u00e9loign\u00e9 de la pr\u00e9sence de Sa\u00fcl, fils de Kis. Ils faisaient partie des vaillants hommes qui lui pr\u00eat\u00e8rent leur secours pendant la guerre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2","name":"1 Chroniques 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.11.47","name":"1 Chroniques 11:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.11.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:2","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9taient des archers, lan\u00e7ant des pierres de la main droite et de la main gauche, et tirant des fl\u00e8ches avec leur arc: ils \u00e9taient de Benjamin, du nombre des fr\u00e8res de Sa\u00fcl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3","name":"1 Chroniques 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.1","name":"1 Chroniques 12:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:3","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le chef Achi\u00e9zer et Joas, fils de Schemaa, de Guibea; Jeziel, et P\u00e9leth, fils d\u2019Azmaveth; Beraca; J\u00e9hu, d\u2019Anathoth;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4","name":"1 Chroniques 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2","name":"1 Chroniques 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:4","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Jischmaeja, de Gabaon, vaillant parmi les trente et chef des trente; J\u00e9r\u00e9mie; Jachaziel; Jochanan; Jozabad, de Gued\u00e9ra;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5","name":"1 Chroniques 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3","name":"1 Chroniques 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:5","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\u00c9luza\u00ef; Jerimoth; Bealia; Schemaria; Schephathia, de Haroph;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6","name":"1 Chroniques 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4","name":"1 Chroniques 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:6","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Elkana, Jischija, Azareel, Jo\u00e9zer et Jaschobeam, Kor\u00e9ites;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7","name":"1 Chroniques 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5","name":"1 Chroniques 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:7","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Jo\u00e9la et Zebadia, fils de Jerocham, de Guedor.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8","name":"1 Chroniques 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6","name":"1 Chroniques 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:8","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Parmi les Gadites, des hommes vaillants partirent pour se rendre aupr\u00e8s de David dans la forteresse du d\u00e9sert, des soldats exerc\u00e9s \u00e0 la guerre, arm\u00e9s du bouclier et de la lance, semblables \u00e0 des lions, et aussi prompts que des gazelles sur les montagnes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9","name":"1 Chroniques 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7","name":"1 Chroniques 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:9","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\u00c9zer, le chef; Abdias, le second; \u00c9liab, le troisi\u00e8me;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10","name":"1 Chroniques 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8","name":"1 Chroniques 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:10","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mischmanna, le quatri\u00e8me; J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le cinqui\u00e8me;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11","name":"1 Chroniques 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9","name":"1 Chroniques 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:11","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Atta\u00ef, le sixi\u00e8me; \u00c9liel, le septi\u00e8me;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10","name":"1 Chroniques 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:12","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Jochanan, le huiti\u00e8me; Elzabad, le neuvi\u00e8me;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13","name":"1 Chroniques 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11","name":"1 Chroniques 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:13","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le dixi\u00e8me; Macbanna\u00ef, le onzi\u00e8me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14","name":"1 Chroniques 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:14","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9taient des fils de Gad, chefs de l\u2019arm\u00e9e; un seul, le plus petit, pouvait s\u2019attaquer \u00e0 cent hommes, et le plus grand \u00e0 mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15","name":"1 Chroniques 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13","name":"1 Chroniques 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:15","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Voil\u00e0 ceux qui pass\u00e8rent le Jourdain au premier mois, lorsqu\u2019il d\u00e9bordait sur toutes ses rives, et qui mirent en fuite tous les habitants des vall\u00e9es, \u00e0 l\u2019orient et \u00e0 l\u2019occident.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16","name":"1 Chroniques 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14","name":"1 Chroniques 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:16","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il y eut aussi des fils de Benjamin et de Juda qui se rendirent aupr\u00e8s de David dans la forteresse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17","name":"1 Chroniques 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15","name":"1 Chroniques 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:17","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>David sortit au-devant d\u2019eux, et leur adressa la parole, en disant: Si vous venez \u00e0 moi dans de bonnes intentions pour me secourir, mon c\u0153ur s\u2019unira \u00e0 vous; mais si c\u2019est pour me tromper au profit de mes ennemis, quand je ne commets aucune violence, que le Dieu de nos p\u00e8res le voie et qu\u2019il fasse justice!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18","name":"1 Chroniques 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16","name":"1 Chroniques 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:18","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Amasa\u00ef, l\u2019un des principaux officiers, fut rev\u00eatu de l\u2019esprit, et dit: Nous sommes \u00e0 toi, David, et avec toi, fils d\u2019Isa\u00ef! Paix, paix \u00e0 toi, et paix \u00e0 ceux qui te secourent, car ton Dieu t\u2019a secouru! Et David les accueillit, et les pla\u00e7a parmi les chefs de la troupe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19","name":"1 Chroniques 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17","name":"1 Chroniques 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:19","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Des hommes de Manass\u00e9 se joignirent \u00e0 David, lorsqu\u2019il alla faire la guerre \u00e0 Sa\u00fcl avec les Philistins. Mais ils ne furent pas en aide aux Philistins; car, apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre consult\u00e9s, les princes des Philistins renvoy\u00e8rent David, en disant: Il passerait du c\u00f4t\u00e9 de son ma\u00eetre Sa\u00fcl, au p\u00e9ril de nos t\u00eates.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20","name":"1 Chroniques 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18","name":"1 Chroniques 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:20","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Quand il retourna \u00e0 Tsiklag, voici ceux de Manass\u00e9 qui se joignirent \u00e0 lui: Adnach, Jozabad, Jedia\u00ebl, Mica\u00ebl, Jozabad, \u00c9lihu et Tsiltha\u00ef, chefs des milliers de Manass\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21","name":"1 Chroniques 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19","name":"1 Chroniques 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:21","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ils pr\u00eat\u00e8rent leur secours \u00e0 David contre la troupe (des pillards Amal\u00e9cites), car ils \u00e9taient tous de vaillants hommes, et ils furent chefs dans l\u2019arm\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22","name":"1 Chroniques 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20","name":"1 Chroniques 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:22","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Et de jour en jour des gens arrivaient aupr\u00e8s de David pour le secourir, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il e\u00fbt un grand camp, comme un camp de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23","name":"1 Chroniques 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21","name":"1 Chroniques 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:23","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Guerriers des douze tribus qui se rendirent \u00e0 H\u00e9bron pour \u00e9tablir David roi<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-40: cf. (1 Ch 11. 2 S 5:1-5.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Voici le nombre des hommes arm\u00e9s pour la guerre qui se rendirent aupr\u00e8s de David \u00e0 H\u00e9bron, afin de lui transf\u00e9rer la royaut\u00e9 de Sa\u00fcl, selon l\u2019ordre de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24","name":"1 Chroniques 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22","name":"1 Chroniques 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:24","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Fils de Juda, portant le bouclier et la lance, six mille huit cents, arm\u00e9s pour la guerre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25","name":"1 Chroniques 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23","name":"1 Chroniques 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:25","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Des fils de Sim\u00e9on, hommes vaillants \u00e0 la guerre, sept mille cent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26","name":"1 Chroniques 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24","name":"1 Chroniques 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:26","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Des fils de L\u00e9vi, quatre mille six cents;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27","name":"1 Chroniques 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25","name":"1 Chroniques 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:27","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>et Jehojada, prince d\u2019Aaron, et avec lui trois mille sept cents;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28","name":"1 Chroniques 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26","name":"1 Chroniques 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:28","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>et Tsadok, vaillant jeune homme, et la maison de son p\u00e8re, vingt-deux chefs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29","name":"1 Chroniques 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27","name":"1 Chroniques 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:29","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Des fils de Benjamin, fr\u00e8res de Sa\u00fcl, trois mille; car jusqu\u2019alors la plus grande partie d\u2019entre eux \u00e9taient rest\u00e9s fid\u00e8les \u00e0 la maison de Sa\u00fcl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30","name":"1 Chroniques 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28","name":"1 Chroniques 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:30","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Des fils d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, vingt mille huit cents, hommes vaillants, gens de renom, d\u2019apr\u00e8s les maisons de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31","name":"1 Chroniques 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29","name":"1 Chroniques 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:31","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>De la demi-tribu de Manass\u00e9, dix-huit mille, qui furent nominativement d\u00e9sign\u00e9s pour aller \u00e9tablir roi David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32","name":"1 Chroniques 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30","name":"1 Chroniques 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:32","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Des fils d\u2019Issacar, ayant l\u2019intelligence des temps pour savoir ce que devait faire Isra\u00ebl, deux cents chefs, et tous leurs fr\u00e8res sous leurs ordres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33","name":"1 Chroniques 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31","name":"1 Chroniques 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:33","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>De Zabulon, cinquante mille, en \u00e9tat d\u2019aller \u00e0 l\u2019arm\u00e9e, munis pour le combat de toutes les armes de guerre, et pr\u00eats \u00e0 livrer bataille d\u2019un c\u0153ur r\u00e9solu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34","name":"1 Chroniques 12:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32","name":"1 Chroniques 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:34","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>De Nephthali, mille chefs, et avec eux trente-sept mille, portant le bouclier et la lance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35","name":"1 Chroniques 12:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33","name":"1 Chroniques 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:35","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Des Danites, arm\u00e9s pour la guerre, vingt-huit mille six cents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36","name":"1 Chroniques 12:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34","name":"1 Chroniques 12:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:36","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>D\u2019Aser, en \u00e9tat d\u2019aller \u00e0 l\u2019arm\u00e9e et pr\u00eats \u00e0 combattre: quarante mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37","name":"1 Chroniques 12:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35","name":"1 Chroniques 12:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:37","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Et de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du Jourdain, des Rub\u00e9nites, des Gadites, et de la demi-tribu de Manass\u00e9, avec toutes les armes de guerre, cent vingt mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38","name":"1 Chroniques 12:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36","name":"1 Chroniques 12:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:38","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Tous ces hommes, gens de guerre, pr\u00eats \u00e0 combattre, arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 H\u00e9bron en sinc\u00e9rit\u00e9 de c\u0153ur pour \u00e9tablir David roi sur tout Isra\u00ebl. Et tout le reste d\u2019Isra\u00ebl \u00e9tait \u00e9galement unanime pour faire r\u00e9gner David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39","name":"1 Chroniques 12:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37","name":"1 Chroniques 12:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:39","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.012.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Ils furent l\u00e0 trois jours avec David, mangeant et buvant, car leurs fr\u00e8res leur avaient pr\u00e9par\u00e9 des vivres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.40","name":"1 Chroniques 12:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38","name":"1 Chroniques 12:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.40","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 12:40","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.012.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.013.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.12.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Et m\u00eame ceux qui habitaient pr\u00e8s d\u2019eux jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Issacar, \u00e0 Zabulon et \u00e0 Nephthali, apportaient des aliments sur des \u00e2nes, sur des chameaux, sur des mulets et sur des b\u0153ufs, des mets de farine, des masses de figues s\u00e8ches et de raisins secs, du vin, de l\u2019huile, des b\u0153ufs et des brebis en abondance, car Isra\u00ebl \u00e9tait dans la joie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12","name":"1 Chroniques 12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.13.1","name":"1 Chroniques 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.13.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39","name":"1 Chroniques 12:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.12.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb34bc408.83211168');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bc408.83211168\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb34bc408.83211168","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb34bc408.83211168'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb34bc408.83211168\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}